{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"dkfh510xhhdkee9koyvnfc0","title":"Fcitx5","desc":"","updated":1663610610080,"created":1663609400125,"custom":{},"fname":"linux.customization.sway.fcitx5","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"bb3e75b19fafdbd20264ca57db2247eb","links":[],"anchors":{"fcitx---langugae-input":{"type":"header","text":"Fcitx - langugae input","value":"fcitx---langugae-input","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"install":{"type":"header","text":"Install","value":"install","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"setup-ubuntu-2004":{"type":"header","text":"Setup (ubuntu 20.04)","value":"setup-ubuntu-2004","line":35,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ct2spb1vqxg4baqenuf40as","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"fcitx5\">Fcitx5<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fcitx5\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"fcitx---langugae-input\">Fcitx - langugae input<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#fcitx---langugae-input\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Install_Fcitx_5\">https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Install_Fcitx_5</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Search on Ubuntu apt: <code>apt-cache search fcitx5</code></li>\n<li>install\n<pre><code>sudo apt-get install fcitx5\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Vietnamese support:\n<pre><code>wget http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/f/fcitx5-unikey/fcitx5-unikey_5.0.8-1_amd64.deb\nsudo dpkg -i fcitx5-unikey_5.0.8-1_amd64.deb\nsudo apt --fix-broken install\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Install FE\n<pre><code>sudo apt install fcitx5-frontend-gtk3\nsudo apt install fcitx-config-gtk\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Input_method_engines#Vietnamese\">https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Input_method_engines#Vietnamese</a>\n<a href=\"https://pkgs.org/search/?q=fcitx5-unikey\">https://pkgs.org/search/?q=fcitx5-unikey</a>\n<a href=\"https://ubuntu.pkgs.org/22.04/ubuntu-universe-amd64/fcitx5-unikey_5.0.8-1_amd64.deb.html\">https://ubuntu.pkgs.org/22.04/ubuntu-universe-amd64/fcitx5-unikey_5.0.8-1_amd64.deb.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"setup-ubuntu-2004\">Setup (ubuntu 20.04)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#setup-ubuntu-2004\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Setup_Fcitx_5#im-config_.28Debian.2FDebian-based.2FUbuntu.29\">https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Setup_Fcitx_5#im-config_.28Debian.2FDebian-based.2FUbuntu.29</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Run <code>im-config</code> &#x26; select fcitx5 </li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/